feedback.text: Your work the past few months has been amazing! You really care about your work and you seem to really take the time to do it the best you can
I just wanted to highlight the hard work you've put into my project
I wanted to congratulate you on your determination to finish this project.
You always work so passionately to make sure our customers get the best experience and insight and they really are reaping the rewards from your efforts! I love working collaboratively with you
You're always so authentic and enthusiastic. So glad you've had some great feedback from customers too as it's so deserved
